Voidface desktop app (Tauri) — scaffold placeholder.

The desktop app is a Tauri 2.x shell around the shipped runtime under
`../../runtime/`. It embeds:

  - `../../runtime/coreml/` on macOS (Apple Neural Engine),
  - `../../runtime/onnx/` on Windows and Linux (ONNX Runtime).

The UI is drag-and-drop image or video, one Protect button, and a
side-by-side before/after preview with PSNR / SSIM / LPIPS readouts.
No accounts, no telemetry, all local.

This directory is intentionally empty until Phase R5. See
`../../Documentation/architecture.md`.
